  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the antihypertensive effect of AGSCT101 tablet in
      patient with stage 1 to 2 essential hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is 2,8 weeks, multi-center, randomized, double-blind, active clinical trial to
      evaluate the efficacy and safety of AGSCT101 versus Carvedilol in patient with stage 1 to 2
      essential hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
